{
  "application": "LAMMPS",
  "details": {
    "software": [
      "podman",
      "LAMMPS",
      "MPICH",
      "Kokkos",
      "CUDA",
      "NVIDIA persistenced",
      "SLURM"
    ],
    "resources": [
      "GPU",
      "CPU",
      "MPI",
      "network",
      "disk space",
      "shared memory"
    ],
    "environment variables": [
      "MPICH_GPU_SUPPORT_ENABLED",
      "LD_PRELOAD",
      "OMP_NUM_THREADS",
      "LD_LIBRARY_PATH",
      "PODMAN_FLAGS",
      "PODMAN_EXEC_FLAGS",
      "IMAGE"
    ],
    "libraries": [
      "libmpi_gtl_cuda.so.0",
      "Kokkos"
    ],
    "file system": [
      "/tmp",
      "/run/nvidia-persistenced",
      "/opt/workdir"
    ],
    "execution": [
      "srun",
      "podman-mpi-exec"
    ],
    "configuration": [
      "in.run",
      "files/*",
      "log._NREP_"
    ],
    "slurm directives": [
      "-C gpu",
      "-t 00:45:00",
      "-J LAMMPS_SNAP_podman_exec",
      "-o LAMMPS_SNAP_podman_exec.o%j",
      "-A nstaff_g",
      "-n _NTASKS_",
      "--cpus-per-task=32",
      "--gpus-per-task=1",
      "--gpu-bind=none",
      "-q early_science"
    ]
  }
}
